見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果個情況其實係咪緊握扶手都無用?<br />\n上面有人跌落黎喎<br />\n<br />\n唔識 鳩估</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜你覺得自己緊握扶手，上面落緊黎條友就炒唔低你？<br />\n緊握扶手去硬食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首先唔講電梯同扶手既運作係咪分日開 當佢地係一樣 咁但係你捉唔捉扶手你都係硬食架啦 唔通你跳梯咩</blockquote><br />\n而家講緊個個都緊握 硬食條毛咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇下上面個人講緊個假設係咩先啦 盲既搭你老母屎忽窿個咀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ff42081c0b83fe164ce6b2d16e8f70db3cf007","tid":174714,"uid":94663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:35:28.000Z","msg":"唔講上面堆人跌緊落黎 發生意外個陣 我諗你唔緊握扶手 第一飛落去個個就係你 做下一步既大前提 就等企穩左再講la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60b045369ccfd2f84b2f6759399c97bd3b9af16","tid":174714,"uid":17397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未遇過電梯壞，但試過扶手突然唔郁電梯照行<br />\n前面果個縮唔切手跌親撞埋嚟<br />\n想問扶手同電梯係未分開運作？<br />\n萬一電梯加速或者急停扶實扶手有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n扶手同電樓梯唔同步，系物業管理公司問題<br />\nuser唔緊握扶手，系user問題</blockquote><br />\n系你老母"},{"pid":"5211bc2e497323dafe92af58432edc7b6dee95cc","tid":174714,"uid":33429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"有種既視感<br />\n成日有單車友話頭盔無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28ccc2b4ab6badc547c8b74fb39dab7c1229159","tid":174714,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"係緊握<br />\n平時d人掂都唔掂，或者只係放隻手扶下就算<br />\n咁都有講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095d12eaec41177be015f70d03159f66996705c1","tid":174714,"uid":35927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:42:26.000Z","msg":"記者咁問黎拎sound bit